You can create extra users with custom permissions to manage their client portal. You must create a role before you create a user.

**Create Role**

Login to the client portal.
Go to Menu >> User/Role Management.
Click on button Add a user or role 
Then click on Roles.
Select the roles from the list and then save the role.

**Create Users**

Once the role is created then click on Users
Complete the form with a username, password and select the role for that user. 
Then click on the OK (tick) button to create a new user on that role.
